      <div n="4" type="section">
        <head>§ 4.</head>
        <p id="p4-1">
          From the
          <ref target="measure-0000000398572267">nineteenth measure</ref>
          until the
          <ref target="measure-0000000135352827">first repetition sign</ref>
          the bass indicates already that the right hand can make use of the bass' preceding
          progressions, about which to loose more words is not necessary.
        </p>
      </div>

