      </div>

      <div n="9" type="section">
        <head>§ 9.</head>
        <p id="p9-1">
          Although this arpeggio appears to be in two voice, is basically in four voice
          and in a quick tempo it sounds even more full than normally eight voices
          as straight-forward and plain chords. But one shall never play it except where
          the bass is alone or where the music is strong.
        </p>
